entries.arrived_at_delivery: One of our gunboats will pick up the unconscious pilot. Stand by.
entries.arrived_at_pickup: The crew on the freighter have subdued the pilot of the experimental fighter and packed him up. Dock with them so they can transfer him to your ship.
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.docking_complete_delivery: The transfer was successful. We're out of here. You should return to Ezkiel pilot.
entries.docking_complete_pickup: Alright. We've loaded the pilot in to your cargo hold. Returning to Corellia.
entries.docking_started_delivery: We're docking now. Stand by for immediate transfer of the experimental model.
entries.docking_started_pickup: Good to see you pilot. We would deliver the pilot ourselves if this was anywhere but the Dathomir system. Traveling around here with an unarmed freighter is asking for trouble.
entries.failed_destroyed: Nooo! We needed that body pilot! Return to base immediately!
entries.found_loc_d: Alright, pilot. You need to deliver the "cargo" to this spot. We're with you, pilot.
entries.found_loc_p: The freighter with the captured ship will meet you at this point, pilot. You'll proceed to dock with them and pickup our information.
entries.hello_d: We'll be docking with you soon. Stand by.
entries.hello_p: Glad to see you, pilot. Stand by for docking.
entries.quest_dock1_d: Dock with the freighter and transfer the 'pilot' to your cargo hold. He's sealed in a life support system and should be fine.
entries.quest_dock1_t: Dock and transfer the unconscious pilot.
entries.quest_dock2_d: If the surrounding area is clear of enemies, dock and transfer the pilot to our gunboat.
entries.quest_location_d: We've picked areas of the Dathomir system that should be light on enemy presence but the Empire is looking for you so right now, nothing is safe.
entries.quest_rendezvous1_d: Meet up with our freighter at these coordinates.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: We have sent one of our heavily guarded gunboats to this area, deliver the pilot to them immediately.
entries.title: Dathomir system: Help transfer experimental pilot.
entries.title_d: Our freighter with the ship is heading for Corellia where it can be examined closely. We want to have a look at the pilot right away though and need your assistance in moving it from the freighter to one of our gunboats in the Dathomir system.
